1. First of all copy this folder in your system (Must not be in the cd or Pendrive).

2. Open a Terminal (Ctrl + T) and move to this Directory.

3. Then Type This Command 
	chmod 0777 install

4. Then Type this
	./install

5. For the First time Your system must me connected to internet to download the required packages.

6. After typing ./install then project will automatically run after few moments.
